title: Fusion Vibes Disposable Nitrile Gloves, Latex Free, Powder Free, Blue, Extra Strong, Multi-Purpose Gloves, Disposable, Medical Grade, Surgical Gloves, Non-Sterile, Single Use - LARGE (Pack of 200)
features: ✅【Disposable Nitrile Gloves】: Protect your hands from any nasty bacteria with the most skin-friendly vinyl single use gloves. Completely Powder free, Natural Latex, Rubber & Protein Free, these multipurpose gloves are perfect for an array of uses without causing the slightest discomfort. A safe choice even for people with skin sensitivities or those allergic to rubber and latex.
✅ 【Latex Free & Powder Free】: These latex-free nitrile gloves are ideal for individuals with latex allergies or sensitive skin. The powder-free design ensures a clean, residue-free experience.

✅【Multi-Purpose & Versatile Gloves】: Comfortable fit with textured fingertips for excellent tactile sensitivity. Disposable gloves useful for lab work, hair salons, food prep, painting, cleaning, or any other jobs where protection of the hand is required.

✅【Disposable Nitrile Gloves Blue】: Nitrile gloves ideal solution for individuals sensitive to natural rubber latex and donning powder. Comfortable fit with textured fingertips for excellent tactile sensitivity.
✅【Durable AND Comfortable Gloves】: Extraordinary strength, stretchable durability, Comfortable & puncture resistance with premium blue color.
✅【Medical Grade Gloves】: These Nitrile Gloves disposable have EN455 compliant and CE approved. Premium Quality - Durable and puncture resistant Nitirle Disposable Gloves.
✅ 【Textured Fingertips Enhanced Grip】: The textured fingertips improve grip and control, making these gloves perfect for precise work in medical, dental, automotive, tattoo, or food service settings.

✅【Ambidextrous Fitting】: Form fitting with an ambidextrous design, these single-use gloves are extremely easy to put on and remove without taking a toll on your dexterity. Coming in a great value-pack of 200 gloves, in a handy dispenser box for easy use and storage, you will always have access to a fresh pair of protective gloves.
